'command2'                             after  each command                 c,p,v,label (note 2)
'create-optional-menus'                (note 8)                            c (note 8)
'create-popup-menu-items'              in tree.OnPopup                     c,p,v,event (new)
'draw-outline-box'             yes     when drawing +- box                 tree,p,v,x,y
